The constraint body does not look grammatical to me. The variable names are not ideal either, I would replace added_property_entity by qualifier_entity and property_entity by statement_entity to emphasize their roles. How about this for the title and body:
Invalid value for qualifier {qualifier_entity} on statement {statement_entity}
On items such as {example_entity}, an invalid value for qualifier {qualifier_entity} was supplied on statement {statement_entity}.

